data.description: Located in beautiful Crowfield Plantation, 178 Bridgecreek Dr is a charming  property that offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Situated in the heart of Goose Creek, this home presents an excellent opportunity for homebuyers or investors looking for a property in the area.This 3 bedroom 2 bath home boasts a thoughtfully designed floor plan and modern features, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a comfortable living space. With an inviting curb appeal, the property exudes warmth and elegance from the moment you arrive.Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by a spacious and open living area that provides plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment. The interior is filled with natural light, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere throughout.The kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar, making meal preparation a breeze. 178 Bridgecreek Dr offers three well-appointed bedrooms, providing comfortable accommodations for both residents and guests. The master suite boasts a private ensuite bathroom and a generous closet, offering a peaceful retreat at the end of a long day. The additional bedrooms share a well-appointed bathroom, ensuring convenience and privacy for all. The property's outdoor space is equally impressive, featuring a spacious backyard that provides ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the beautiful South Carolina weather. The backyard also offers the potential for creating a personalized outdoor oasis or entertaining space. All of this and a roof installed 2015, HVAC installed 2016, Master Bath remodel in 2019, second bath remodel in 2020, new dishwasher in 2021, new stove - 2020, new washer - 2020 and dryer - 2020. Conveniently located, this home provides easy access to a range of amenities and attractions. Nearby, you'll find shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and recreational facilities, ensuring that all your daily needs are within reach. The property also offers excellent proximity to major roadways, allowing for convenient commuting to other parts of Goose Creek or nearby cities.
